      "level": 3,
      "class": "Sample",
      "biography": "<p>Demonstrates <strong>non-proficiency</strong>. The mage is proficient only with club, dagger, dart, and staff, and wears no armour. The Staff attacks normally; the Sword is equipped but untrained, so attacking with it takes the RAW −1 penalty (shown in the chat card's total) and gains no fighting-style benefit. The armour cap is <em>unarmored</em>, so wearing the leather is flagged as beyond proficiency.</p>"
